<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَلَعْنُهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَحَلْبُهَا مَا يَضُرُّ بِوَلَدِهَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَضَرْبُ وَجْهٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَوَسْمٌ فِيهِ، وَيَجُوزُ فِي غَيْرِهِ لِغَرَضٍ صَحِيحٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَتَجِبُ الحَضَانَةُ لِحِفْظِ:</span> صَغِيرٍ، وَمَجْنُونٍ، وَمَعْتُوهٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَالأَحَقُّ بِهَا:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> أُمٌّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> ثُمَّ أُمَّهَاتُهَا، القُرْبَى فَالقُرْبَى.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> ثُمَّ أَبٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> ثُمَّ أُمَّهَاتُهُ كَذَلِكَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> ثُمَّ جَدٌّ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> ثُمَّ أُمَّهَاتُهُ كَذَلِكَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٧]</span> ثُمَّ أُخْتٌ لِأَبَوَيْنِ، ثُمَّ لِأُمٍّ، ثُمَّ لِأَبٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
